`,n(e.p,{children:["In addition, ",n(e.a,{href:"/docs/advanced/speculative-module-fetching/",children:"Speculative Module Fetching"})," enables Qwik to prioritize the important parts of interactivity before the less important parts."]}),`
`,n(e.p,{children:['For example, the "',n(e.em,{children:"Buy Now"}),'" button is more important than the "',n(e.em,{children:"Add to Cart"}),'" button, so Qwik will prefetch the "',n(e.em,{children:"Buy Now"}),'" button first, and then the "',n(e.em,{children:"Add to Cart"}),'" button.']}),`
`,n(e.p,{children:["Qwik does not need to prefetch everything to start running, while other frameworks do need to download the whole critical path before they can start running because of ",n(e.a,{href:"https://www.builder.io/blog/hydration-is-pure-overhead",children:"hydration"}),"."]}),`
