`,n(e.p,{children:["Not at all! Thanks to ",n(e.a,{href:"/docs/advanced/speculative-module-fetching/",children:"Speculative Module Fetching"})," Qwik apps are not more affected by slow networks than other frameworks. In fact, because of the fine-grained bundling and resumability, Qwik apps can become interactive with much less JS, effectively making them faster on slow networks."]}),`
